      "content": "exactly. it feels way more targeted than just \"ads\" though. like i'm starting to think they aren't just collecting data, they are actually testing specific responses on me to see how much they can influence my mood or my behavior. if they're already doing this with the lighting and the temp, what else are they actually monitoring in my house right now?",
